This is the very first time I have purchased a calendar. It’s not like I never had a calendar at home - it’s just that either it was gifted by someone or it was a complimentary one. You can say that this was a self-gift and absolutely a great one. 
Pure coincidence but the calendar arrived on 1st January 2025 and it felt like, finally, 2025 has to be ‘MY’ year then. 🤍
This is the ‘Ganga Calendar Gift Box’ from @phool.co 🌱 I have always been fascinated by the products they curate for their audience but I was like a little too fascinated by this Ganga calendar. The calendar is a thematic inspiration from the ‘Gond-inspired’ art and a flowing progression on every page which illustrates a part of the river, from her origin to the estuary. 🌊✨💛

~
